job.title: RSMSSB Patwari Recruitment 2021 – Apply Online for 5378 vacancies in Rajasthan
job.body:
Total vacancies:5378

Name of the Vacancies:

  • Patwari

Description

Latest Central Government Jobs for Graduates have been published by Rajasthan Subordinate and Ministerial Services Selection Board for Patwari vacancies in Rajasthan. If you are searching for a government job in Rajasthan then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of Patwari, from the 15-07-2021, and till 29-07-2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in Rajasthan and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.

Application fee:

  • The mode of application is Online
  • No information about application fee

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for a Patwari in RSMSSB, your Graduation must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates:

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is 15-07-2021
  •  The last date to apply in these posts is 29-07-2021 

Age Limit Criteria:

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 28 years old. 

RSMSSB Patwari Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the location Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is as per norms

How to apply for tRSMSSB Patwari Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process the Patwari. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of RSMSSB and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by RSMSSB 
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.
